msgctxt "an5.223:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.223:0.2"
msgid "23. Dīghacārikavagga "
msgstr "23. Long Wandering "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.223:0.3"
msgid "223. Atinivāsasutta "
msgstr "223. Overstaying "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.258, sc1
msgctxt "an5.223:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, ādīnavā atinivāse. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five drawbacks of overstaying. "

msgctxt "an5.223:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.223:1.3"
msgid "Bahubhaṇḍo hoti bahubhaṇḍasannicayo, bahubhesajjo hoti bahubhesajjasannicayo, bahukicco hoti bahukaraṇīyo byatto kiṅkaraṇīyesu, saṃsaṭṭho viharati gahaṭṭhapabbajitehi ananulomikena gihisaṃsaggena, tamhā ca āvāsā pakkamanto sāpekkho pakkamati. "
msgstr "You have a lot of stuff and store it up. You have a lot of medicine and store it up. You have a lot of duties and responsibilities, and become capable in whatever needs to be done. You mix closely with laypeople and renunciates, socializing inappropriately like a layperson. And when you leave that monastery, you miss it. "

msgctxt "an5.223:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ādīnavā atinivāse. "
msgstr "These are the five drawbacks of overstaying. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an5.223:2.1"
msgid "Pañcime, bhikkhave, ānisaṃsā samavatthavāse. "
msgstr "There are these five benefits of staying for a reasonable length of time. "

msgctxt "an5.223:2.2"
msgid "Katame pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.223:2.3"
msgid "Na bahubhaṇḍo hoti na bahubhaṇḍasannicayo, na bahubhesajjo hoti na bahubhesajjasannicayo, na bahukicco hoti na bahukaraṇīyo na byatto kiṅkaraṇīyesu, asaṃsaṭṭho viharati gahaṭṭhapabbajitehi ananulomikena gihisaṃsaggena, tamhā ca āvāsā pakkamanto anapekkho pakkamati. "
msgstr "You don’t have a lot of stuff and store it up. You don’t have a lot of medicine and store it up. You don’t have a lot of duties and responsibilities, or become capable in whatever needs to be done. You don’t mix closely with laypeople and renunciates, socializing inappropriately like a layperson. And when you leave that monastery, you don’t miss it. "

msgctxt "an5.223:2.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ānisaṃsā samavatthavāse”ti. "
msgstr "These are the five benefits of staying for a reasonable length of time.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.223:2.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

